headline: 3 No-Brainer Dividend Stocks to Buy With $2,000 Right Now
summary: Prologis has grown its dividend much faster than the S&P 500 and the average REIT.  Invitation Homes has hiked its payout every year since it went public in 2017.  NNN REIT has raised its dividend for 35 straight years.
